0669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c13998ef3ed4319154d8a120d213e574e12273c6","tid":1913222,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"播毒俠"},{"pid":"07cc8945ce3327c34acc69bd365e4c3e1a8b538f","tid":1913222,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"三俠"}]}